questions = read.csv("../TAREAS_R/questions.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",", dec = ".")

tags = read.csv("../TAREAS_R/tags.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",", dec = ".")

questions_with_tags = questions %>%
